Error: Error: "Internal Exception: Io.Netty.Handler.Codec.EncoderException" 

This Error Occurs When The Communication Between Your Computer And The Minecraft Server Is Disrupted, Usually Due To A Connection Issue.

Step-By-Step

Solution: 1. First, make sure that your internet connection is stable and strong enough to play online. You can check your connection speed by running a speed test online.

2. If your connection is problematic, try restarting your modem/router or contacting your internet service provider (ISP).

3.
